tyle=\"margin:0;font-size:13px;color:#6b7280;line-height:1.5;\">At BestSecurity, we have protected over 20,000 households and 1,500 businesses in Denmark since 2017. We aim to give you peace of mind and secure your digital life.</p></td></tr></table><p style=\"margin:24px 0 4px;font-size:15px;color:#374151;\">Best regards,</p><p style=\"margin:0;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:#1f2937;\">{{ booker }}</p><p style=\"margin:2px 0 0;font-size:13px;color:#9ca3af;\">BestSecurity</p>",
